{
  "body": {
    "id": "lastchance01",
    "rows": [
      {
        "id": "header01",
        "columns": [
          {
            "id": "headercol",
            "width": 100,
            "contents": [
              {
                "type": "image",
                "id": "logoimg",
                "values": {
                  "src": {
                    "url": "https://cameronestateinn.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Cameron-Estate-Logo.png",
                    "width": 180,
                    "height": 60,
                    "maxWidth": "50%",
                    "autoWidth": false
                  },
                  "alt": "Cameron Estate Inn",
                  "width": 200,
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "padding": "20px 0"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "values": {
          "backgroundColor": "#2C3E50",
          "padding": "0 0 0 0"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "opening01",
        "columns": [
          {
            "id": "opencol01",
            "width": 100,
            "contents": [
              {
                "type": "heading",
                "id": "head01",
                "values": {
                  "text": "{{contact.first_name}},",
                  "tag": "h2",
                  "color": "#2C3E50",
                  "fontFamily": "Cormorant Garamond",
                  "fontSize": 28,
                  "fontWeight": 500,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 15px 0"
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "text01",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p>I haven't heard from you in a bit, so I'm assuming you've likely found your wedding venue or decided to go in a different direction.</p>",
                  "color": "#4A4A4A",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 15px 0"
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "text02",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p>I just wanted to send one last note to say: <strong>congratulations</strong>.</p>",
                  "color": "#4A4A4A",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 15px 0"
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "text03",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p>Planning a wedding is a big journey. Wherever you've chosen to celebrate, I truly hope it's everything you've envisioned. I hope the day is full of joy, that the weather is perfect, and that you're surrounded by people who love you.</p>",
                  "color": "#4A4A4A",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 15px 0"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "values": {
          "backgroundColor": "#FDFCFA",
          "padding": "40px 40px 20px 40px"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "body01",
        "columns": [
          {
            "id": "bodycol01",
            "width": 100,
            "contents": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "text04",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p>If you <em>are</em> still looking and just haven't had a chance to reply — life gets busy! — I'm still here. You can always reach back out to me, even months from now. If we have the date available, we'd love to host you.</p>",
                  "color": "#4A4A4A",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 15px 0"
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "text05",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p>But for now, I'll take you off my follow-up list so I'm not clogging your inbox.</p>",
                  "color": "#4A4A4A",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 25px 0"
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "sig01",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p style=\"font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 500; color: #2C3E50;\">All the best,<br/>Lisa</p>",
                  "color": "#2C3E50",
                  "fontFamily": "Cormorant Garamond",
                  "fontSize": 22,
                  "fontWeight": 500,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 0 0"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "values": {
          "backgroundColor": "#FFFFFF",
          "padding": "30px 40px 30px 40px"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "footer01",
        "columns": [
          {
            "id": "footercol01",
            "width": 50,
            "contents": [
              {
                "type": "image",
                "id": "footerlogo",
                "values": {
                  "src": {
                    "url": "https://cameronestateinn.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Cameron-Estate-Logo.png",
                    "width": 180,
                    "height": 60,
                    "maxWidth": "50%",
                    "autoWidth": false
                  },
                  "alt": "Cameron Estate Inn",
                  "width": 150,
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "padding": "0 0 10px 0"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "footercol02",
            "width": 50,
            "contents": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "footertext",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p style=\"font-family: 'Poppins', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #666666; text-align: center; line-height: 1.6;\"><strong>Cameron Estate Inn</strong><br/>1495 Monterey Road<br/>Middletown, PA 17057<br/><br/><a href=\"https://cameronestateinn.com\" style=\"color: #2C3E50; text-decoration: none;\">cameronestateinn.com</a></p>",
                  "color": "#666666",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 12,
                  "lineHeight": 1.6,
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "padding": "0 0 0 0"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "values": {
          "backgroundColor": "#FFFFFF",
          "padding": "30px 40px 30px 40px"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "footer02",
        "columns": [
          {
            "id": "footer2col",
            "width": 100,
            "contents": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "unsubscribe",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p style=\"font-family: 'Poppins', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; color: #999999; text-align: center;\">You received this email because you're on our mailing list. <a href=\"{{links.unsubscribe}}\" style=\"color: #999999; text-decoration: underline;\">Unsubscribe</a></p>",
                  "color": "#999999",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 11,
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "padding": "0 0 0 0"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "values": {
